# A widely [[cultivated]] [[plant]], {{taxlink|Solanum lycopersicum|species}}, having [[edible]] [[fruit]]
# The savory [[fruit]] of this plant, red when ripe, treated as a [[vegetable]] in [[horticulture]]
#* Note: The US Supreme Court in [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nix_v._Hedden ''Nix v. Hedden'' (1893)] ruled that a tomato is a vegetable.
# A shade of [[red]], the colour of a ripe tomato.
# {{context|slang}} A desirable-looking woman.
